%% F1-15 · DLQ Error Flow
%% Sequence: worker fails → envelope publish → DLQ peek with error → requeue extracts originalMessage

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Queue as Origin Queue
    participant Worker
    participant Publisher as IQueuePublisher
    participant DLQ as DLQ Queue
    participant Admin
    participant API
    participant DlqService

    Note over Queue,Worker: Normal processing fails after max retries

    Worker->>Queue: Receive message
    Worker->>Worker: Process (throws Exception)
    Worker->>Worker: Retry 1, 2, 3... all fail
    Worker->>Publisher: PublishToDlqAsync(queue, originalMessage, ex)
    Publisher->>Publisher: Build envelope { originalMessage, error }
    Publisher->>Publisher: Truncate error.message to 2000 chars
    Publisher->>DLQ: Publish envelope JSON

    Note over Admin,DlqService: Admin views DLQ

    Admin->>API: GET /api/admin/dlq?queue=parser
    API->>DlqService: PeekMessagesAsync
    DlqService->>DLQ: Peek messages
    DLQ-->>DlqService: Raw body (envelope)
    DlqService->>DlqService: Parse envelope, extract error
    DlqService-->>API: DlqPeekResult with error populated
    API-->>Admin: Response with error.message, error.type

    Note over Admin,DlqService: Admin requeues message

    Admin->>API: POST /api/admin/dlq/{queue}/{id}/requeue
    API->>DlqService: RequeueMessageAsync
    DlqService->>DLQ: Receive message (delete from DLQ)
    DlqService->>DlqService: Parse body
    alt Envelope format
        DlqService->>DlqService: Extract originalMessage
        DlqService->>Queue: Publish originalMessage
    else Legacy format
        DlqService->>Queue: Publish raw body
    end
    DlqService-->>API: Success
    API-->>Admin: 200 OK

    Note over Queue,Worker: Worker receives and processes again
